snippet.title: Trailer ☆ WAR LEGENDS. Mobile RTS
snippet.description:
Welcome to the official War Legends YouTube channel where you'll find all the latest videos, news and content!

War Legends — is a classic fantasy real-time strategy game on your mobile device.
Large-scale battles, heroes with unique abilities, and powerful magic scrolls are waiting for you.

Testing has begun! Get the game now:
☆ Android: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.geargames.warlegends.rts.strategy.game
☆ iOS: https://testflight.apple.com/join/RBbbx0rU
Install the game on TestFlight.
☆ If the game is not available in your country you can download the APK file: https://redirect.appmetrica.yandex.com/serve/532429537204528559

🔔 To stay up to date, be sure to subscribe above and check back often for the new trailers, in-game moments, streams and more.

Useful links:
Visit the War Legends Official website: https://warlegends.geargames.org/en/
Join our Facebook Fans: https://facebook.com/warlegendsrts
Check out the War Legends community on Discord: https://discord.com/invite/SbuJ2YAsPw
